{
  "texts": [
    "Medicine is no different.",
    "The framework within this paper cannot solve the entire problem of xAI.",
    "However, that is not our goal.",
    "Rather, we aim to formulate a set of standards for xAI that would be sufficient for their ethical deployment in healthcare, and this can be considered an improvement over the current state of affairs.",
    "There has been a long and controversial debate about the nature of medical reasoning in medical sciences since it is a concept investigated by different disciplines with different aims (cognitive psychology, medical education, philosophy of science, etc.)"
  ]
}